### Zero Trust IAM — API Test Requests
### Install the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client) to run these
### Usage: click "Send Request" above any request block

@base_url = http://localhost:8000
@keycloak  = http://localhost:8080
@realm     = zero-trust-demo
@client_id = policy-engine
@secret    = policy-engine-secret

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 1. Health checks
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name health_policy
GET {{base_url}}/health

###

# @name health_risk
GET http://localhost:8001/health

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 2. Get tokens from Keycloak
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name analyst_token
POST {{keycloak}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id={{client_id}}&client_secret={{secret}}&username=analyst_bob&password=Analyst@123!&scope=openid

###

# @name engineer_token
POST {{keycloak}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id={{client_id}}&client_secret={{secret}}&username=engineer_alice&password=Engineer@123!&scope=openid

###

# @name admin_token
POST {{keycloak}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id={{client_id}}&client_secret={{secret}}&username=admin_user&password=Admin@123!&scope=openid

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 3. Authorization requests — ALLOW scenarios
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name allow_analyst_read_reports
# Paste analyst token below (from request #analyst_token above)
POST {{base_url}}/api/authorize
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ANALYST_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource": "finance-reports",
  "action": "READ"
}

###

# @name allow_engineer_read_db
POST {{base_url}}/api/authorize
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ENGINEER_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource": "prod-database",
  "action": "READ"
}

###

# @name allow_admin_user_mgmt
POST {{base_url}}/api/authorize
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource": "user-management",
  "action": "WRITE"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 4. Authorization requests — DENY scenarios
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name deny_analyst_write_reports
POST {{base_url}}/api/authorize
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ANALYST_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource": "finance-reports",
  "action": "WRITE"
}

###

# @name deny_analyst_prod_database
POST {{base_url}}/api/authorize
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ANALYST_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource": "prod-database",
  "action": "READ"
}

###

# @name deny_engineer_delete_db
POST {{base_url}}/api/authorize
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ENGINEER_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resource": "prod-database",
  "action": "DELETE"
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 5. Events & stats (dashboard data)
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name get_events
GET {{base_url}}/api/events?limit=20

###

# @name get_deny_events_only
GET {{base_url}}/api/events?decision=DENY&limit=10

###

# @name get_stats
GET {{base_url}}/api/events/stats

###

# @name get_sessions
GET {{base_url}}/api/sessions

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 6. Policy management
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name list_all_policies
GET {{base_url}}/api/policies

###

# @name list_analyst_policies
GET {{base_url}}/api/policies?role=analyst

###

# @name create_new_policy
POST {{base_url}}/api/policies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "analyst-read-audit-logs-extended",
  "role": "analyst",
  "resource": "audit-logs",
  "action": "READ",
  "effect": "ALLOW",
  "allowed_hours_start": 7,
  "allowed_hours_end": 19,
  "max_risk_score": 45
}

### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### 7. Risk engine direct test
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# @name score_normal_request
POST http://localhost:8001/score
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "test-user-001",
  "username": "analyst_bob",
  "ip_address": "127.0.0.1",
  "user_agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux x86_64)"
}

###

# @name score_suspicious_request
POST http://localhost:8001/score
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "test-user-suspicious",
  "username": "unknown",
  "ip_address": "45.33.32.156",
  "user_agent": "curl/7.68.0"
}
